放時間亦配合提早至早上9時開放。田氏重申，稍後加推單位有一定加價空間。田氏指，發展項目第二期仍準備樓書當中，與合作伙伴仍商討推盤期。<br />\n<br />\n信置營業部助理總經理朱美儀介紹，發展項目會所命名GRAND CENTRAL PARK，設施分布兩期，室內外總面積近10萬平方呎，提供室外泳池、室內泳池、多用途運動場、健身室、兒童遊樂室、宴會廳、共享閱讀空間等等。發展商稱，預計每呎管理費約3.98元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb831da654e4efc87ffe53459ef621167fe3963","tid":936902,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"邊個會買海傲灣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e18f65792fa2a337177fb4945ec970a45673f1","tid":936902,"uid":470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ffb831da654e4efc87ffe53459ef621167fe3963","tid":936902,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"邊個會買海傲灣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"麥包"},{"pid":"6af052bdf92eefc82b02bc40ef2a28fc4cff6c3e","tid":936902,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97e18f65792fa2a337177fb4945ec970a45673f1","tid":936902,"uid":470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ffb831da654e4efc87ffe53459ef621167fe3963","tid":936902,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"邊個會買海傲灣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"麥包"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"環海東岸仲未入伙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f4ed794cfc5973cf58374a5a597d70cef4290c","tid":936902,"uid":6297